The perInstance currently looks like:
```nix
perInstance = { instanceName, extendSettings, ... }:
  {
    nixosModule = ...
```

Add `exports` to advertise the vaultwarden endpoint. The port comes from `localSettings.ROCKET_PORT` (defaults to 8222). You need to compute the port BEFORE the nixosModule so it's available for exports. Add:
```nix
perInstance = { instanceName, extendSettings, ... }:
  let
    baseSettings = extendSettings {
      ROCKET_PORT = lib.mkDefault 8222;
    };
    serverPort = baseSettings.ROCKET_PORT or 8222;
  in
  {
    exports.serviceEndpoints.vaultwarden = {
      url = "http://localhost:${toString serverPort}";
      port = serverPort;
    };
    nixosModule = ...  # keep existing nixosModule unchanged
```

